      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-06-29T16:40:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e Despite being ignored for external management, these interfaces still require `runtime IP configuration` for reliable BMC communication. Since no DBus objects exist for ignored interfaces, we use direct ioctl ystem calls to configure them.\n\nPlease highlight \"runtime config\" in the commit message",
      "parentUuid": "bc1715fa_6cdf996c",
      "revId": "c78a2516c1de252b8c79e86d81e3f748b9c3be85",
